txt.en: You have completed your mission and should talk to the Dumûri Scout.
Rescue the prisoners being held in Eshadûr and save them from the Ordâkhai torturer Dokhára.
The Ordâkhai torturer Dokhára is holding several Ambarûli people prisoner in Eshadûr.
'I'm glad you were able to help Mushendu. I've been dispatched to bring you back to Urmâkh, there are other matters there that require your attention.'
You have rescued the prisoners being held in Eshadûr. Now you must face the Ordâkhai torturer Dokhára.
Defeat Dokhára on the path towards the Entrance
'Thank you for your help, [placeholder]! The people are safe now, thanks to you.'
